&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Advisory&amp;nbsp;Department&lt;/strong&gt; of one of the fastest-growing accounting firms in the country is seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Business Transformation Manager&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;who is motivated to learn, excited to collaborate and passionate about delivering outstanding results. This individual will have a direct impact on our firm’s mission of serving as a catalyst for those striving to achieve their highest potential.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
