&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Diagnose constraints across process, people, systems, structure, economics, strategy, data, and decision-making. Lead development of recommendations, business cases, and implementation plans.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
