&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;This role requires discretion, strong documentation and analytical skills, and the ability to handle confidential and complex credentialing tasks while exemplifying a high standard of professionalism and customer service.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
